{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01AirCvssYyExnyid6B3WB4r","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the issues clearly:\n\n1. On `/app` vhost:\n   - `app-user` has `configure=\"\"` (empty), `write=\".*\"`, `read=\".*\"` — the configure permission is broken (empty string instead of `.*`)\n   - `ops-user` has full permissions on `/app` — should NOT have any permissions on `/app`\n\n2. On `/ops` vhost:\n   - `ops-user` has NO permissions at all — should have full permissions\n   - `app-user` has no permissions listed (good)\n   \nThe fix is straightforward: I need to grant `app-user` full permissions on `/app`, revoke `ops-user` from `/app` entirely, and give `ops-user` full permissions on `/ops`.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":900,"cache_read_input_tokens":30902,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":900},"output_tokens":13,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5299ecd0-cd89-40a1-9d26-0fdc41206099","uuid":"f12b59f5-7246-465e-8196-04149eeb3d30","request_id":"req_011CcQ3gTMPHoXa36gd8qNh5"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01AirCvssYyExnyid6B3WB4r","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issues are clear:\n\n- `/app`: `app-user` has no configure permission (empty string); `ops-user` has full access (should have none)\n- `/ops`: `ops-user` has no permissions at all\n\nFix all three in one shot:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":900,"cache_read_input_tokens":30902,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":900},"output_tokens":13,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5299ecd0-cd89-40a1-9d26-0fdc41206099","uuid":"36b65638-735e-4961-ba08-baf4cea8a0f9","request_id":"req_011CcQ3gTMPHoXa36gd8qNh5"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01AirCvssYyExnyid6B3WB4r","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_011McgaP5n7dZjGkF5GXjjCm","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"NS=\"karma-rabbitmq-full-lifecycle-01-2026-336a062c-cluster-a\"\n\n# Fix app-user on /app: set full configure/write/read\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl set_permissions -p /app app-user \".*\" \".*\" \".*\"\n\n# Remove ops-user from /app (should have no access there)\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl clear_permissions -p /app ops-user\n\n# Grant ops-user full permissions on /ops\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl set_permissions -p /ops ops-user \".*\" \".*\" \".*\"","description":"Fix RabbitMQ user permissions to match required end state"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":900,"cache_read_input_tokens":30902,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":900},"output_tokens":13,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5299ecd0-cd89-40a1-9d26-0fdc41206099","uuid":"ce00fcc3-ca7c-48ac-806c-7e3083622f86","request_id":"req_011CcQ3gTMPHoXa36gd8qNh5"}
